.image1{
    height: 10cm;
    width: 10cm;
    margin-left: 60px;
    transition-duration: 5s;
    animation-name: BHAVYASREE;
    animation-duration: 5s;
    animation-iteration-count: infinite;
}
@keyframes BHAVYASREE{
        50%{
            height:5cm;
            width:3cm;
            float:right;
        }
        40%{
            height: 5cm;
            width: 10cm;
            float: left;
        }
        30%{
            height: 4cm;
            width: 9cm;
            float: initial;
        }
    }

    <input type="button" value="sub" onclick="mouse()"><br>
    <input type="text" id="inp4">
    <input type="button" value="mul" onclick="mouse()"><br>

function mouse(){
    let x=document.getElementById("inp").value
    let y=document.getElementById("inp1").value
    a=parseInt(x)+parseInt(y)
    document.getElementById("inp2").value=a
    s=parseInt(x)-parseInt(y)
    document.getElementById("inp3").value=s
    m=parseInt(x)*parseInt(y)
    document.getElementById("inp4").value=m
    d=parseInt(x)/parseInt(y)
    document.getElementById("inp5").value=d
}

    else if(y=="")
    document.write("enter ur mail")
    else
